      "text": "**Rigours, plural - Meta-rigour and choreography**\n\nEach quadrant of the dance schema is home to numerous modes of rigour, appropriate to\n- the kind of engagement (left-side object/right-side subject)\n- the mode of action (below the line in-the-body, above the line in-language) and \n- the material particularity of the ‘stuff’ being engaged.\n\n"
    },
