      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "6095adcf8e31ae99",
      "text": "Examining this, we also may highlight the way in which dealing with matters of rigour - which are central in the §2 cultural landscape of knowing and capability - lifts us out of the cultural landscape, and into the §3 **aesthetic** landsape."
