        "text": "**Curious features of code**\nThe formalised rigour of code and formal machine-performable scripts (as software code, as algorithm) is a particularly powerful - and problematic - feature of the dance of knowing in the present century.  The cultural landscape §2 has acquired enormously and newly powerful means of determining the **material** landscape §1. This warrants a specific note, following.\n"
